replies.bodyText:
I think both the CloseableHttpResponse and the CloseableHttpClient should be closed.
https://hc.apache.org/httpcomponents-client-ga/tutorial/html/fundamentals.html shows the following:
CloseableHttpResponse response = httpclient.execute(httpget);
try {
    <...>
} finally {
    response.close();
}

Also FreeIpaClientBuilder::connect() does a close on both the CloseableHttpResponse and the CloseableHttpClient.

